Testmod for FME (Full Model Emulation) online output processing.

Enables horizontal remapping, vertical coarsening, and derived diagnostics
for EAM, MPAS-Ocean, and MPAS-Sea-Ice.

Designed for ACE/Samudra coupled model emulation training data generation.
See shell_commands for map file generation instructions.

## Running tests

  cd cime/scripts
  ./create_test SMS_Ld2_P512.ne30pg2_r05_IcoswISC30E3r5.WCYCL1850 --testmod allactive/fme_output
  ./create_test SMS_Ld2_P512.ne30pg2_r05_IcoswISC30E3r5.WCYCL1850 --testmod allactive/fme_legacy_output

## Verification

Run from the repo root. Requires micromamba env with xarray, matplotlib, cartopy, netCDF4.

  # EAM verification (standalone)
  micromamba run -n xgns python \
    cime_config/testmods_dirs/allactive/fme_output/verify_eam.py \
    --rundir /path/to/fme_output_case/run \
    --outdir /path/to/output_figs

  # EAM cross-verification (FME vs legacy)
  micromamba run -n xgns python \
    cime_config/testmods_dirs/allactive/fme_output/verify_eam.py \
    --rundir /path/to/fme_output_case/run \
    --legacy-rundir /path/to/fme_legacy_output_case/run \
    --outdir /path/to/output_figs

  # MPAS-Ocean and MPAS-SeaIce verification
  micromamba run -n xgns python \
    /pscratch/sd/m/mahf708/e3sm-repo/mahf708-e3sm/cime_config/testmods_dirs/allactive/fme_output/verify_mpas.py \
    --rundir /path/to/fme_output_case/run \
    --outdir /pscratch/sd/m/mahf708/aifigs_v3LRpiControlSamudrACE

Dashboards are written to:
  <outdir>/verify_eam.html
  <outdir>/verify_mpas.html


